snippet.title: Johnny Depp DEMANDS ACLU SHOW PROOF of Amber Heard's Donation | The Gossipy
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp DEMANDS ACLU SHOW PROOF of Amber Heard's Donation | The Gossipy

Welcome toThe Gossipy. We make interesting videos about Hollywood in English. We give you a closer look in the lives of celebrities like Kanye West, Ed Sheeran, The Rock, Jay Z, Selena Gomez, Kylie Jenner, Kim Kardashian, Rihanna and 100s more.

While some celebrities prefer living a quiet life away from the public, others just have so many scandals following them. In this video, we are going to talk about Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, who have been on each other’s throats ever since they split up and how Amber Heard could be caught in a lie.

Johnny Depp has to pay Amber Heard several million in a divorce settlement. Amber Heard said she donated that money to the ACLU because she never wanted Johnny Depp's money. However, many suspected this was not true. Amber might get caught in another lie.  

We break it all down in our latest video. Do not forget to like, comment, and subscribe.

#AmberHeardJail​ #AmberHeard​ #AmberHeardCourt​ #JusticeForJohnny #JusticeforJohnnyDepp

We tell you interesting things about these Hollywood celebrities that you may have never heard before.
